為住院真係必買<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/eeltk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feeltk&d=nOKVOrQ%2BeJKlB8hxaAzPoTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=45046fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/eeltk</a>"},{"pid":"0ddaa9254490d3e4e6889f1cfe3bd3ca776bd797","tid":780103,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:53:26.000Z","msg":"買份醫療最緊要<br />\n可以傾下比較多幾間公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ThirteenChung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FThirteenChung&d=nOKVOrQ%2BeJKlB8hxaAzPoTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2aaba2d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ThirteenChung</a>"},{"pid":"111a78686328890a1e2a67c99ab76bac26d603b3","tid":780103,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"保險狗空群而出，係得呢度 R 生意你真係覺得佢地有料？"}]}